▁in ▁fact ▁, ▁even ▁though ▁a ▁city ▁prior ▁to ▁the ▁edo ▁period ▁would ▁have ▁been ▁designed ▁to ▁match ▁the ▁shi jin - so - o ▁topography ▁, ▁it ▁is ▁very ▁unlike ly ▁that ▁the ▁four ▁gods ▁were ▁mountain ▁, ▁river ▁, ▁road ▁and ▁lake ▁.
