▁the ▁other ▁ball ads ▁in ▁the ▁same ▁period ▁were ▁of ▁the ▁kind ▁inscribed ▁on ▁the ▁monument ▁of ▁bus sok use k ika ▁in ▁yakushi - ji ▁temple ▁in ▁nara ▁and ▁" ▁kin ka fu ▁, ▁" ▁which ▁was ▁a ▁book ▁on ▁the ▁wagon ▁( ▁a ▁japanese ▁string ▁instrument ▁, ▁also ▁called ▁the ▁yamat og oto ▁, ▁that ▁consisted ▁of ▁a ▁flat ▁, ▁shallow ▁sound ▁box ▁with ▁six ▁strings ▁, ▁much ▁like ▁a ▁z ither ▁) ▁, ▁was ▁copied ▁in ▁the ▁middle ▁of ▁the ▁heian ▁period ▁.
