▁manyoshu ▁contains ▁about ▁45 00 ▁poems ▁, ▁the ▁earliest ▁of ▁which ▁was ▁composed ▁in ▁the ▁reign ▁of ▁emperor ▁nintoku ▁, ▁but ▁most ▁of ▁them ▁were ▁being ▁made ▁during ▁the ▁period ▁of ▁less ▁than ▁100 ▁years ▁from ▁the ▁asuka ▁period ▁to ▁the ▁middle ▁of ▁the ▁nara ▁period ▁.
