▁in ▁its ▁process ▁, ▁waka ▁gradually ▁regained ▁its ▁position ▁as ▁an ▁official ▁culture ▁along ▁with ▁the ▁development ▁of ▁kana ▁characters ▁( ▁the ▁japanese ▁syllab aries ▁) ▁, ▁and ▁uta ▁aw ase ▁( ▁poetry ▁match ▁) ▁came ▁to ▁be ▁held ▁.
▁in ▁the ▁book ▁of ▁" ▁shinsen ▁manyoshu ▁( ▁newly ▁selected ▁manyoshu ▁) ▁, ▁" ▁japanese ▁poems ▁were ▁put ▁beside ▁the ▁chinese ▁poems ▁, ▁which ▁suggested ▁that ▁the ▁japanese ▁poetry ▁was ▁regain ing ▁its ▁status ▁as ▁an ▁official ▁literature ▁.
▁under ▁such ▁circumstances ▁, ▁" ▁kokin ▁wakashu ▁( ▁collection ▁from ▁ancient ▁and ▁modern ▁times ▁) ▁, ▁" ▁the ▁first ▁anthology ▁of ▁japanese ▁poetry ▁compiled ▁by ▁imperial ▁command ▁, ▁was ▁made ▁and ▁offered ▁to ▁the ▁emperor ▁.
