▁compared ▁with ▁the ▁conservative ▁" ▁go ▁shui ▁wakashu ▁, ▁" ▁the ▁following ▁" ▁kin yo ▁wakashu ▁( ▁a ▁collection ▁of ▁golden ▁leaves ▁) ▁" ▁was ▁innov ative ▁and ▁focused ▁on ▁fresh ▁descri pt ive ▁poems ▁; ▁however ▁, ▁the ▁subsequent ▁" ▁shika ▁wakashu ▁( ▁a ▁collection ▁of ▁ver bal ▁flowers ▁of ▁japanese ▁poetry ▁) ▁" ▁marked ▁a ▁return ▁to ▁the ▁conservative ▁style ▁.
