▁it ▁shows ▁a ▁tendency ▁toward ▁the ▁principle ▁of ▁art ▁for ▁art ▁' s ▁sake ▁in ▁the ▁destruction ▁of ▁the ▁aristocracy ▁and ▁the ▁rise ▁of ▁samurai ▁warriors ▁, ▁elev ating ▁the ▁status ▁of ▁waka ▁in ▁the ▁late ▁heian ▁period ▁.
▁the ▁following ▁" ▁shin ▁kokin ▁wakashu ▁( ▁new ▁collection ▁of ▁ancient ▁and ▁modern ▁japanese ▁poetry ▁) ▁" ▁was ▁compiled ▁and ▁dedicated ▁to ▁the ▁emperor ▁by ▁toshinari ▁' s ▁disciple ▁.
