▁since ▁around ▁the ▁period ▁of ▁the ▁northern ▁and ▁southern ▁courts ▁( ▁japan ▁) ▁, ▁waka ▁came ▁to ▁be ▁composed ▁mainly ▁by ▁monks ▁and ▁samurai ▁, ▁while ▁the ▁composition ▁of ▁waka ▁spread ▁to ▁local ▁samurai ▁, ▁and ▁some ▁of ▁the ▁waka ▁that ▁l ap sed ▁into ▁formal ism ▁declined ▁.
