▁history
▁in ▁1899 ▁, ▁kyoto ▁college ▁of ▁textile ▁f ib ers ▁was ▁founded ▁.
▁in ▁1902 ▁, ▁kyoto ▁college ▁of ▁technology ▁was ▁founded ▁.
